                            <comment id="17779574" author="jlewandowski" created="Wed, 25 Oct 2023 16:42:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The issue can be demonstrated with this CQL:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-sql&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;CREATE&lt;/span&gt; KEYSPACE ks &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;WITH&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;REPLICATION&lt;/span&gt; = {&lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;class&apos;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;SimpleStrategy&apos;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;replication_factor&apos;&lt;/span&gt;: 1};
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;CREATE&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; ks.tab (id &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;INT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;PRIMARY&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;KEY&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;INT&lt;/span&gt;, b &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;INT&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;c&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;INT&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;INSERT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;INTO&lt;/span&gt; ks.tab (id, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;a&lt;/span&gt;, b, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;c&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;VALUES&lt;/span&gt; (1, 1, 1, 1);
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; ks.tab &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;DROP&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;c&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;INSERT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;INTO&lt;/span&gt; ks.tab (id, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;a&lt;/span&gt;, b) &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;VALUES&lt;/span&gt; (2, 2, 2);
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;ALTER&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;TABLE&lt;/span&gt; ks.tab &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;ADD&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;c&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;INT&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;INSERT&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;INTO&lt;/span&gt; ks.tab (id, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;a&lt;/span&gt;, b, &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;c&lt;/span&gt;) &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;VALUES&lt;/span&gt; (3, 3, 3, 3);
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; * &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; ks.tab;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;restart the node, then&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-sql&quot;&gt;
&lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;SELECT&lt;/span&gt; * &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;FROM&lt;/span&gt; ks.tab;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17856407" author="krummas" created="Thu, 20 Jun 2024 07:32:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;pushed an alternative patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/cassandra/pull/3380&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt; which is less invasive - it just stores the execution time in the &lt;tt&gt;AlterSchema&lt;/tt&gt; transformation&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17899102" author="beobal" created="Mon, 18 Nov 2024 10:22:45 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Rebased the patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=marcuse&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;marcuse&quot;&gt;marcuse&lt;/a&gt; linked to and added a bump to the metadata serialization version. &lt;br/&gt;
CI looks decent too, so I think this is more or less where it needs to be. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17899161" author="krummas" created="Mon, 18 Nov 2024 14:40:47 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;lgtm, +1&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17901444" author="beobal" created="Wed, 27 Nov 2024 10:38:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;After rebase CI looks even better, 1 python dtest failure in &lt;tt&gt;largecolumn_test.py::TestLargeColumn::test_cleanup&lt;/tt&gt;. Seems to repro very occasionally when run locally.&lt;/p&gt;
